---> PRESENT SIMPLE TENSE
DO		I WE YOU THEY
Q --> do you go on holiday every summer?
A --> yes, I go on holiday every summer
N --> no, I don't go on holiday every summer
DOES		HE SHE IT
Q --> does he/she go on holiday every summer?
A --> yes, he/she goes on holiday every summer
N --> no, he/she doesn't go on holiday every summer


	the sun sets in the West. 				güneş batıdan batar					- Genel Doğru
	I play tennis.						tenis oynarım						- Hobi
	she hates broccoli.					o brokoliden nefret eder				- Sevmediklerimiz
	he works in a bank. 					o bir bankada çalışır					- Rutin
	I drink coffee every morning.				her sabah kahve içerim					- Alışkanlık
	the plane arrives at 10:30.				uçak 10:30’da varacak					- Saat çizelgelerinde
	the prince gets on his horse.				prens atına biner					- Hikaye anlatımı
	you heat the oven to a temperature of 180 degree.	fırını 180 dereceye kadar ısıtın			- Talimat

	Present Simple Signals:
		every day/week/month/year	(her ...)				I go walking in the morning every day
		Adverbs of Frequency		(Sıklık Zarfları)
		now and then			(ara sıra, bazen, zaman zaman)
		first ... then ...		(ilk ... ondan sonra ...)		first i get on a bus, then i get to work 
                these days                      (bu günlerde)
			I live in Ankara these days					--> Present Simple
			I have been living in Ankara these days (for a few months)	--> Present Perfect Continuous
			

